wiki.content: “Cobra” sees Megan share her raw and intense portrayal of emotional pain, depression, and the complexities of personal relationships as well as her confidence and resilience. A day before the release of the track, the artist posted the meaning of the symbolism in the title “Cobra” Cobra: Cobras exemplify courage and self reliance. They stand tall and herse in the face of challanges, teaching one to tap into their inner strengih and rely on oneself to conquer their threats. Emulating the cobra helps one be more confident in the person they are within. The track was first teased on October 13, 2023, when Megan posted a series of cryptic pictures adding up to the name ‘ACT ONE’ with the caption ‘Lets🐍’. This was followed by a post of a short video of the intro to the official music video on October 26, 2023. She later confirmed the track’s title and release date. Read more on Last.fm.
